Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}食べなきゃダメだってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（子龍）ピッ… ピイイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ピイッ ピイイ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あっ…
